		<title>The Route to an Aviation Career.</title>
		<link>http://www.fearoflanding.com/misc/the-route-to-an-aviation-career/</link>
		<comments>http://www.fearoflanding.com/misc/the-route-to-an-aviation-career/#comments</comments>
